author: Zach Dennis
title: Is Tom Cruise considering a Florida move?
text:
Following the massive success of his most recent movie, “Mission Impossible: Rogue Nation,” is Tom Cruise making a move to Florida? The rumor mill is hot with gossip.
After putting his $59 million mansion in Beverly Hills up for sale, Us Weekly reports that Cruise is considering relocating to the Sunshine State. US Weekly added that Cruise may be looking to relocate to Clearwater where Scientology's spiritual headquarters is located.
Tom Cruise So, will Mr. Cruise become a Floridian? We'll just have to wait and see.
Read more at Us Weekly .
